um's top step.\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 367, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9971626756041139, \"rank\": 0.0028453976733520334, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Capewell\", \"score\": 0.999997246383526, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sophie Capewell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Capewell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Capewell\"}, {\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"score\": 0.9999776191133415, \"rank\": 2.1985825373004267e-05, \"text\": \"Emma\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"opening night\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 331}, {\"ngram\": \"Saint-Quentin-en\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"Yvelines\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 365}, {\"ngram\": \"no time\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 406}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's team\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"trio\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"ofKaty Marchant\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"as many hours\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"route\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium's top step\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their final ride of 45.186 seconds was flawless, New Zealand beaten into silver and world champions Germany forced to settle for bronze.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 