e next cycle\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea that their first Olympic ride in a dozen years would also be the fastest in history, though, was probably not on his mind.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2766}, {\"ngram\": \"their first Olympic ride\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"a dozen years\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2813}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2850}, {\"ngram\": \"his mind\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions Incredible days out and trips for autumn and winter The caveat here is that the team sprint in this three-rider format is relatively new, only adopted in major championships post-Tokyo and up from two on the Olympic programme for the first time here.\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 3344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3022, \"end\": 3038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proud\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Games Sports quiz\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2969}, {\"ngram\": \"100 hard questions\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Slam Track decision\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3070}, {\"ngram\": \"2025 ambitions\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3089}, {\"ngram\": \"trips\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3119}, {\"ngram\": \"autumn\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3130}, {\"ngram\": \"winter\", \"from\": 3135, \"t